        "notes": "Kartick has had ongoing issues related to attendance and work discipline. A formal advisory was issued, and HR has been involved to ensure the matter is properly documented. As Kartick is based in CDG, Sameer also had a face-to-face discussion with him following the first incident.\n\nMore recently, Kartick requested two days of PTO without providing the required two weeks\u2019 prior notice, which again highlights concerns around adherence to process. If such instances repeat, we will move him to the next stage of the CMS process and begin evaluating a replacement."
